347ŌåÆ/**
348ŌåÆ * Create an HTTP server that:
349ŌåÆ * - Proxies /api/* and /ws to the backend
350ŌåÆ * - Serves static frontend files for everything else
351ŌåÆ * - Injects the backend port into the frontend config
