  1ŌåÆ/**
  2ŌåÆ * Build script for @deus/cli
  3ŌåÆ *
  4ŌåÆ * 1. Bundle the CLI TypeScript ŌåÆ dist/cli.js (esbuild)
  5ŌåÆ * 2. Copy pre-built bundles into bundles/ for distribution:
  6ŌåÆ *    - agent-server.bundled.cjs (from apps/agent-server/dist/)
  7ŌåÆ *    - server.bundled.cjs (from apps/backend/dist/)
  8ŌåÆ *    - web/ (from dist/web/ ŌĆö built by `bun run build:web`)
  9ŌåÆ *
 10ŌåÆ * Prerequisites: run these from the monorepo root before building the CLI:
 11ŌåÆ *   bun run build:agent-server
 12ŌåÆ *   bun run build:backend
 13ŌåÆ *   bun run build:web
 14ŌåÆ */
